@namespace PgmStudio.Client.Pages.AuthoringParts

<section class="ds-section" id="tree">
  <div class="ds-section-heading">
    <div>
      <p class="ds-kicker">07</p>
      <h2>Generated region tree</h2>
    </div>
    <p>For intent maps the shaping steps drop the tree — structure is an artifact. It lives here, in the
       Regions activity, read-only: the inspection &amp; debug surface for what the generator produced.</p>
  </div>

