  <p class="ds-theming-note">
    The author never touches this tree. Teams emits the spawn cylinders + protect rectangles; Build emits the
    island/bridge rectangles + the void-deny negative; Wools emits the room rectangles + monument points. The
    unions, the negative wrapper, the synthetic <code>__anon_N</code> ids are all structural glue the generator
    produced — not authored decisions. To move a spawn, return to Teams and drag the intent point; the tree
    regenerates on the next save.
  </p>
